# Task done

When the user says **task done**, **done**, **finish**, **complete**, or similar:

**Read and execute [DEFINITION_OF_DONE.md](../../DEFINITION_OF_DONE.md)** — especially **Task done (agent flow)** and **Checklist**. Do not use this rule file for step details; if steps change, they change only in that markdown file.
